2.3 Distance to Mexico (km)
Isolate Mexico from your countries object. Cast to MULTILINESTRING. Compute distance from each city to the Mexican border. Store as dist_to_mexico. Produce a flextable of the 5 cities farthest from Mexico.


Code
mexico_border &lt;- countries_america|&gt;
  filter(admin == "Mexico")|&gt;
  st_cast("MULTILINESTRING")

us_cities &lt;- us_cities|&gt;
  mutate(dist_to_mexico = st_distance(us_cities, mexico_border)|&gt;
      set_units("km"))

us_cities|&gt;
  st_drop_geometry()|&gt;
  slice_max(dist_to_mexico, n = 5)|&gt;
  select(city, state_name, dist_to_mexico)|&gt;
  flextable()|&gt;
    set_header_labels(
    dist_to_mexico = "Distance to Mexico",
    city = "City",
    state_name= "State")|&gt;
  set_caption("Table 1. Five cities farthest from Mexico border")|&gt;
  autofit()


